---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="RoastMyListing - AI Listing Critic" description="AI listing critic. Paste text, get a score, flaw breakdown, and a ready rewrite. Free.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <a href="/en/apps" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">&larr; All apps</a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mt-8 mb-12">
        <img src="/apps/roast-my-listing-icon.png" alt="RoastMyListing icon" width="128" height="128" class="rounded-[28px] shadow-lg" />
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3"><span class="gradient-text">RoastMyListing</span></h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">AI Listing Critic</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Screenshots -->
      <div class="mb-12 overflow-x-auto">
        <div class="flex gap-4 pb-4" style="min-width: max-content;">
          <img src="/apps/roast-my-listing/screenshots/en/screenshot_1.png" alt="Analysis result" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roast-my-listing/screenshots/en/screenshot_2.png" alt="Score breakdown" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roast-my-listing/screenshots/en/screenshot_3.png" alt="Before/after" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roast-my-listing/screenshots/en/screenshot_4.png" alt="Examples" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roast-my-listing/screenshots/en/screenshot_5.png" alt="Paste mode" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roast-my-listing/screenshots/en/screenshot_6.png" alt="Dark mode" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roast-my-listing/screenshots/en/screenshot_7.png" alt="Settings" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          No sales? Your listing is the problem. Paste it — AI roasts every flaw, scores it 1-10, and rewrites it to actually sell. Free. No account. On-device AI — your listing never leaves your phone.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">How It Works</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          1. Choose your platform (Etsy, eBay, Avito, Airbnb, Vinted). 2. Paste your listing text. 3. Tap "Roast It". 4. Get your score, detailed roast, and a ready-to-copy rewrite.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">What You Get</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Photo Roast</strong> — snap a screenshot of any listing. AI reads the text and roasts it instantly. No copy-paste needed</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Score 1-10</strong> — breakdown by Title, Description, Keywords, Emotion, Trust</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Detailed Roast</strong> — every flaw explained with humor and a concrete fix</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Ready Rewrite</strong> — improved title + description, ready to copy-paste</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Any Marketplace</strong> — Etsy, eBay, Amazon, Avito, Vinted, Airbnb, Facebook Marketplace, Depop, Poshmark, OLX</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">On-Device AI</strong> — Apple Intelligence, your listing never leaves your iPhone. Devices without Apple Intelligence use Google Gemini only with your permission</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Before/After Card</strong> — share your roast results as a visual card showing your grade improvement. Perfect for marketplace groups and social media</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Free Forever</strong> — no ads, no subscription, no in-app purchases, no account required. No data collected</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Who It's For</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Etsy sellers wondering why nobody buys their handmade candles. eBay resellers with listings that read like a police report. Airbnb hosts whose "cozy apartment" sounds like every other cozy apartment. Anyone who pasted a listing and thought "looks fine to me." It's not fine. Let's fix it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Coming to App Store</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted">Roast My Listing is preparing for release. Free for iOS.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-3">Text is analyzed on-device via Apple Intelligence. On devices without Apple Intelligence, Google Gemini is used only with your explicit permission. No data is stored.</p>
        <a href="/apps/roast-my-listing/privacy" class="text-sm text-accent-purple hover:underline">Privacy Policy &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">
        <p>Questions or feedback: <a href="mailto:magic4e@gmail.com" class="text-accent-purple hover:underline">magic4e@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
